headline: MYR Group (MYRG) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: MYR (MYRG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +12.64% and +3.84%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
